DESCRIPTION OF MAIN ELEMENTS:
=============================
You play as a nobody form a small Town who wants to become an evil mastermind.
In order to build up your criminal organization you have to hire thugs to steal
form the locals and threaten shopkeepers for protection money.

Your income is required to expand your organization and equip your minions and
evil hideout lair (mom's basement) with new technologies and dig tunnels
through in the underground.

Once you start with your criminal actions there are chances that the police will
track you down on their own, or you get snitched by one of your henchmen.

In case the police finds out about your plans, it will try to infiltrate your
lair through the main entrance or an optional entrance in the sewer.

When the suspicions agains you are rather minor you can solve the problems by
bribing a single person with a lot of money, or eliminate the investigation
team that's on your case.

CONTROLLS AND PLAYER INTERFACES:
================================
The player controlls a strategy camera that can go around everywhere and see
everything.
The keyboard is used for Hotkeys and not required to play the game.
Graphical userinterfaces provide menus to hire and manage henchmen.
Statistics about loyallity and condition of the henchmen are provided in tables.
When directly selecting a henchman the player can controll it's inventory and
give direct orders regarding movement by rightclicking close to a node.
Multiple entities should not be directly controlled by the player, but their AI
should follow general order (like build this). 
For some orders (like heists, special harresments or intimidations) the player 
can select special groups of minions, who shall perform this order.

