SIMULATION:
===========
Without player interaction the game shall simulate a normal small town with low
unorganized crime. Workers going to work and home and stuff...

TECHNOLOGY:
===========
Neither you, nor your goons are very tech savvy people, but you have to rely on
technology (like cellphones) and gadgets (like smokebombs) in order to go on a
successful caper. Your lair also requires protection (like keycard doors)
and life sustainment (like underground air cleaning).
In order to research and install advanced technologies you have to either pay
researchers without morals, or beat up some nerds in the library, until they
help you.
Research and production require money and special goods (like chemicals).
These goods either have to be stolen (from police evidence room, school, lab)
or bought from the black market.
